<br>
There were tons of pics of this kid on a website his father made. pics of him at hooters, in school photos, etc.<br>
<br>
Since hardforum had a LOT of photoshop people there, we took this kids pics and started making changes here and there, making totally new pictures, and generally making fun of the kid, but in our own little place, not making an actual website devoted to making fun of this kid. it was all done in fun, and he may have been referred to as tard in many pictures, but in the end it was done all in good fun.<br>
<br>
Somehow his father found out though, and proceeded to call up every company that was hosting a pic of the kid, and threatened to sue if they were not removed. Most were removed, and the forum suddenly came up with a rule that we needed permission from the people in pictures before we could do anything like that again.<br>
<br>
From that day on you could have someone post a pic of his twin brother and say &quot;photochop my twin brother&quot; and the mods would remove it unless he said &quot;I have his permission&quot;<br>
<br>
or a pic of people in a bar would get posted that said &quot;here is a friend and I, photochop it&quot; but there would be a third person off to the side and the mods would remove it cause it didn't mention having that 3rd persons permission.<br>
<br>
Dwark, it's not that Lurikeen hasn't a sense of humour, you gotta realize some people have a different sense of humour than you do. If my friends sat around making fun of random people all the time and did nothing but that, I'd get pretty sick of them pretty fast.<br>
<br>
Some people don't care one way or another if you want to post their pic on your site and make fun of them, but others do and you could show a little class and remove it if they do get mad. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uaishen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aishen</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 1259<br> <font color=#E9D756>(10/21/02 9:19:31 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> I'm going to lock Siilverain and Igota in my room in dat der house /nodnod. <p>- Aishen<br>
